Still figuring out how to organize blog
- Preview/filter featured, personal, and tech blogs on /blog/ domain
    - Featured blogs pull from both personal, tech, and otherwhere
    - Personal blogs will show as if from /blog/personal/
    - Tech blogs will show as if from /blog/tech/)


- Create static file that lists (in HTML/XML?) the directories of all blog posts
- Update static file with known blog posts
- Use static file to populate an index in each category directory (personal/tech/etc.)


- Could also approach simulating a change in directories to view "new content" (i.e. the blogs belonging to that category) by using a simple URL-spoof by using a hash (i.e. .../blog/#personal/) or the window.history.pushState/replaceState functions in JS


----- HTML to include for filtering tags
<!--Radio inputs to select filter - not shown!-->
<input type="radio" id="featured-radio" class="radio-button" name="content-filter" checked="checked">
<input type="radio" id="personal-radio" class="radio-button" name="content-filter">
<input type="radio" id="tech-radio" class="radio-button" name="content-filter">

<!--Filter buttons-->
<div id="blog-filter">
	<label for="featured-radio" class="filter-label featured">Featured</label>
	<label for="personal-radio" class="filter-label personal">Personal</label>
	<label for="tech-radio" class="filter-label tech">Tech</label>
</div>


----- CSS to include for filtering tags
.radio-button {
    display: none;
}

#blog-filter {
    padding: 5% 0;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
	color: white;
}

.filter-label {
	background-color: #262626;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    font-size: 1.4em;
    text-align: center;
    cursor: pointer;
	flex-grow: 1;
}

.filter-label:hover {
	text-decoration: underline;
}

#featured-radio:checked~#blog-filter .featured,
#personal-radio:checked~#blog-filter .personal,
#tech-radio:checked~#blog-filter .tech {
    background-color: white;
	color: #262626;
	border: 2px solid #262626;
	
}

#tech-radio:checked~main .tech,
#featured-radio:checked~main .featured,
#personal-radio:checked~main .personal {
    display: block;
}